title: Windows 10 Technical Preview build 9841 part 1 of 2
description:
Windows 10 Technical Preview MultiLang pack - murphy78
Part 1 of 2 (build 9841)

This should only be used on a live machine by a technician or by
someone who is technically proficient in helping report issues and
give opinion feedback to MS. You should not be using this as an
end-user system. There will likely be many application compatibility
issues and crashes involved. You've been warned, so proceed at your
own discretion.

I am uploading these so that as wide an audience as possible can
help MS create the best OS they can with Windows 10. I don't make
any money distributing these things either directly or indirectly.

The default Technical Preview and Enterprise Technical Preview are
available in 4 languages only: en-US, en-GB, zh-CN, and pt-BR
Any other languages would likely need to be installed through the
control panel after install. There are no language packs available
for offline integration at this time, and likely will not be for
the duration of the technical preview. I have not tested the product
yet. I have simply verified hashes and inspected files. If you find
an issue with the product, try reporting it with the issue reporting
thing. MS's website for this venture is: http:
